         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">5/10/88. ¶  ¶ It will please you very much, noble Sir, that I have obtained a gentleman resident in subtropical east Australia to collect algae. The locality is a new and — as it seems — rich one! The...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="de">88.10.05</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="de">To Jacob Agardh</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="de">Handskr. Avdl., Universitetsbibliotek, Lund.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="de">5/10/88.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg style="">
                  <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Es wird Sie sehr freuen, edler Herr, dass ich im subtropischen Ost-Australia einen ansässigen Herrn gewonnen habe, Algen zu sammeln. Die Localität ist eine neue und — wie es scheint — reiche! Diese Algen, von denen ich nur eine unvollständige Dubletten-Sammlung für das Regierungs-Herbarium hier zurück-behalte, sind von Mr James Keys an der Mündung des Burnett-Flusses gesammelt. Ich war nur einmal am Burnett-Fluss, 1856, wie ich mit Gregory den Austral Continent (nach 17 monatlicher Abwesenheit von allen Niederlassungen und nachdem wir lange von Fleisch unserer Pack-Pferde gelebt) durchschritten hatte von N.W. nach N.O., zur Zeit wo selbst noch am Burnett-Fluss die Eingebornen sehr feindselig und Cannibalen waren!</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg style="">
                  <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Gönnen Sie mir nach aller Mühe die kleine Freude, dass die interim Namen für die <name key="Cladophora">Cladophora</name> und <name key="Leveillea">Leveillea</name> verbleibt, sollten sich solche etwa als neu erweisen. Harvey that dasselbe. Wir müssen einen so guten Sammler wie Keys encouragiren.</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Besten Dank für Auskunft über <name key="Diuris">Diuris</name>.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="de">Stets der Ihre</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd von Mueller</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">Gewiss werden Sie sich um Weihnacht und Neujahr erfreuen an der Untersuchung dieser Algen.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg style="">
                  <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Im Januar have</seg>
               <note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>habe?</p>
               </note>
               <seg style=""> ich in der therapeutischen Section der Versamml. Austral Aerzte zu praesidiren</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ich bin zum Presidenten der Austr Assoc for advancm. of Science für 1889 gewählt.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>1846 traf ich Steenstrup, Forchhammer Örsted und andere Scandinavier in der Vers. der Naturf. in Kiel</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">5/10/88.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>It will please you very much, noble Sir, that I have obtained a gentleman resident in subtropical east Australia to collect algae. The locality is a new and — as it seems — rich one! These algae, of which I keep back here only an incomplete duplicate collection for the Government Herbarium, are collected by Mr James Keys at the mouth of the Burnett River.<note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Qld. See J. Keys to M, 26 September 1888.</p>
               </note> I was only once at the Burnett River, in 1856<note xml:id="ftn3" type="footnote" n="3">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>During the North Australian Exploring Expedition, 1855-6.</p>
               </note> as I traversed the Austral continent with Gregory (after a 17-month absence from all settlements and after we lived for a long time on meat from our pack horses) from north-west to north-east, at the time when even the Aborigines at the Burnett River were still very hostile and cannibals!</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Grant me after all the trouble the small pleasure that the interim names remain for the <seg style="font-style: italic; ">
                  <name key="Cladophora">Cladophora</name>
               </seg> and <seg style="font-style: italic; ">
                  <name key="Leveillea">Leveillea</name>
               </seg>, should such for instance prove to be new. Harvey did the same. We must encourage such a good collector as Keys.<note xml:id="ftn4" type="footnote" n="4">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <seg style="">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                     </seg>Algaebase (accessed 18 June 2017) contains no <seg style="font-style: italic; ">
                        <name key="Cladophora">Cladophora</name>
                     </seg> or <seg style="font-style: italic; ">
                        <name key="Leveillea">Leveillea</name>
                     </seg> named for Keys; however in Agardh's list of algae collected by Keys at the entrance to the Burnett River (J. Agardh to M, undated (in this edition as 89-00-00b)), specimen number 11 is named as <seg style="font-style: italic; ">
                        <name key="Leveillea">Leveillea</name> Keysii</seg>, with the name attributed to M.</p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Best thanks for the information on <seg style="font-style: italic; ">
                  <name key="Diuris">Diuris</name>
               </seg>.<note xml:id="ftn5" type="footnote" n="5">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>See M to J. Agardh, 14 July 1888, with his request for some information on <seg style="font-style: italic; ">
                        <name key="Diuris">Diuris</name>
                     </seg>.</p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Always your</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von Mueller</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Undoubtedly you will enjoy the investigation of these algae at Christmas and New Year.<note xml:id="ftn6" type="footnote" n="6">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <seg style="">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Filed with this letter is a draft note from Agardh to M reporting that Keys's collection had arrived badly damaged; see J. Agardh to M, undated (in this edition as 88-11-00).</seg>
                  </p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>In January I have to preside in the therapeutic section of the congress of Australian physicians.<note xml:id="ftn7" type="footnote" n="7">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Intercolonial Medical Congress of Australasia, Melbourne, January 1889.</p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I am elected president of the Australasian Association for the Advancement of Science for 1889.<note xml:id="ftn8" type="footnote" n="8">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>The second Congress of the Australasian Association for the Advancement of Science, held in Melbourne in January 1890.</p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>In 1846 I met Steenstrup, Forchhammer, Örsted and other Scandinavians in the Congress of Natural Scientists in Kiel.<note xml:id="ftn9" type="footnote" n="9">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <seg style="">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Versammlung Deutscher Naturforscher und Ärzte, Kiel, September 1846.</seg>
                  </p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="plant%20names" xml:lang="en">
               <name key="Cladophora">Cladophora</name>
            </p>
            <p rend="plant%20names" xml:lang="en">
               <name key="Diuris">Diuris</name>
            </p>
            <p rend="plant%20names" xml:lang="en">
               <name key="Leveillea">Leveillea</name>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
         </div>
      </body>
